spec_data.Name: v4l-utils
spec_data.Description:
v4l-utils is a collection of various video4linux (V4L) and DVB utilities. The
main v4l-utils package contains cx18-ctl, ir-keytable, ivtv-ctl, v4l2-ctl and
v4l2-sysfs-path.
